lemma pair_not_fst: shows "Pair A B \<noteq> Fst P"
proof(transfer)
fix A B P :: "'a ptrm"
show "\<not> PPair A B \<approx> PFst P"
proof(rule classical)
assume "\<not> \<not> PPair A B \<approx> PFst P"
hence False
using pairE
by fastforce
thus?thesis
by blast
qed
qed
